data.title: Garland D. “‘Skeeter'” Wilson (1926
data.meta_description: Garland D. ‘Skeeter' Wilson  ROCHESTER — A celebration of life for Garland D. Skeeter Wilson, 81, Rochester, will be held at 2 p.m. Thursday in Good Family Funeral Home.  He died at 3:15 p.m. Sunday, May 25, 2008, in his residence.  Pastors Larry Dodge and Leonard Jackson will officiate at the services. Burial, with...
